{"tid":1919044,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我宣佈唔好再討論投白票功能組別與否","createTime":"2020-03-10T13:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:04:17.000Z","uid":251732,"like":57,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0255b967f83858c3c0d08b31479cf387e626568a","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔好話我道德勒索， 但希望唔好忘記抗爭最基本原則 <br />\n就係: 不分化不割蓆、不篤灰 不譴責 、有改進 可接受、 以及五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n就算你同我都唔會接受功能組別的存在， 但咁嘅情況大家都要絕地一鋪試下先， 到時真係得咗就用返特權法徹底廢除功能組別制度，同其他五大訴求最重要嘅元素， 尤其係成立獨立調查委員會徹查警黑暴行 、廢除所有違背人權人性嘅惡法、 向獨裁長官施壓撤回定義、以及全面落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n睇下你班水軍仲有乜嘢資格話其他手足係鬼係分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3a9137a281a778964939529c587e8f933f78f6","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"pish 2"},{"pid":"40f18e3dc95854dd901a89197dcd7ddc32ac83eb","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"pish 1"},{"pid":"ab7464c3a73321fe78d24d13600f283799c58f40","tid":1919044,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"好快有人入黎屌尻你邊位"},{"pid":"f1412687771441894fd9b8200ab13b46befe1201","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"pish 3"},{"pid":"e69e992800846793735b71d697ae356eecada079","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7464c3a73321fe78d24d13600f283799c58f40","tid":1919044,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"好快有人入黎屌尻你邊位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"冇話邊位喎大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通喺呢個困局下仲有心情內鬥咩？"},{"pid":"de94652511a98262adad6c2256df54c0c97251e3","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:36:52.0