overnments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"99bc5e53e3e27eb9166e77f1be45fbcecd8647ae","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d8803fee96883977c7b1105b5ccf051fd3bdae","tid":1919044,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb0d7dd7094099394be0066d0b1e6b04cc1ff92","tid":1919044,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d18d9f1d9e0f5819d2311eb62f7f3713161974ed","tid":1919044,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:26:40.000Z","msg":"你睇下你個POST 得我同你9UP咋<br />\n未放棄香港先放棄連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"所以就麻煩咁多位幫幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"鬥到我都想潛咩都唔想做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"咁就更加要將我呢個宣佈話畀所有手足聽"},{"pid":"0054e089569cfcd6ef38acc31a139e5118f01971","tid":1919044,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99bc5e53e3e27eb